Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases that are corrected and resubmitted
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time it takes for a declaration to be 'REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' after being 'APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum time it takes for a declaration to move from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for resubmission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for a declaration to be finalized ('Payment Handled') after being 'REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and then 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' from the initial submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases that include 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to the next activity in the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case
